### By Our Hand

Gardener_1 = {
	name = Garth # Canon, AKA: Greenhand
	dynasty = dynn_Gardener
	dna = Gardener_1

	learning = 9

	religion = old_gods_wnw
	culture = first_man

	trait = education_stewardship_4
	trait = greensight
	trait = patient
	trait = zealous
	trait = diligent
	trait = charming

	disallow_random_traits = yes

	give_nickname = nick_greenhand

	2.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
		add_character_flag = has_scripted_appearance # changed from 1.1.1 to 2.1.1 because the game doesn't like 1.1.1
		add_character_flag = canon_status_canon
	}
	15.1.1 = {
		trait = lustful
		trait = lifestyle_gardener
		trait = family_first
	}
	80.1.1 = { death = yes }
}
